dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners in Langlade County, Wisconsin in 2019. [The Public Land Survey System (PLSS) is a way of subdividing and describing land in the US. All lands in the public domain are subject to subdivision by this rectangular system of surveys. A handy link with a robust description is listed here from the USGS: https://nationalmap.gov/small_scale/a_plss.html.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
